[thinking] **Considering test ordering**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about how testing should be structured after child tests. Maybe after those, the system test could load the real one. If the first test is a direct system test, it would cover Java 9. On the other hand, if an isolated test runs second, that would target Java 8. I want to make sure the tests are organized logically to ensure comprehensive coverage.
